00:52.052 --> 00:53.428
Lord Kaidu.

00:56.181 --> 00:57.683
Welcome to Cambulac.

00:59.685 --> 01:01.394
[gate creaking]

01:11.238 --> 01:13.240
[theme music playing]

01:13.264 --> 01:19.264
Synced and corrected by sysrapmarvel
